  <exercise xml:id="inv3-8-g">
    <title>Observed Value in Null Distribution</title>
    <statement>
      <p>Where does the observed value of the relative risk from the actual study fall in the null distribution of the relative risks? What proportion of the simulated relative risks are at least this extreme?</p>
    <hint>Use the <term index="no">Count Samples</term> button in the applet. Do you want "greater than", "less than", or "beyond"?</hint>
